an><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"n\">Fin</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">z</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">hi</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"n\">ℕ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">≠</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">z</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&lt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">z</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">omega</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\">-- i stands for current row, j stands for specified column, z stands for the last row + 1, p stands for the row of the pivot</span>\n<span class=\"c1\">-- turns all numbers on column j below row i or p into 0</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">turnBelowIntoZero</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">GroupWithZero</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">DecidableEq</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Add</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Neg</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">z</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℕ</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">M</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Matrix</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Fin</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">z</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Fin</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">z</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Fin</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">z</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">j</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Fin</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">z</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Fin</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">z</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Matrix</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Fin</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">z</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Fin</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">z</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"c1\">-- if the current row is the last row, then return matrix</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">z</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">then</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">M</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"c1\">-- if the value of the position below is 0, move onto the next one below</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">else</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">isucc</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"n\">lessSucc</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h1</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Fin</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">z</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">M</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">isucc</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">j</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">then</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">turnBelowIntoZero</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">M</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">isucc</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">j</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"c1\">-- if it is not 0, then make it into 0 and move on to the next one below with the changed matrix</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">else</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">M'</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">addMulRow</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">M</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">isucc</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">M</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">isucc</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">j</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">M</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">j</span><span class=\"o\">))</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">turnBelowIntoZero</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">M'</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">isucc</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">j</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span>\n<span class=\"n\">termination_by</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">z</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"n\">eval</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">turnBelowIntoZero</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">!!</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">3</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span><span class=\"mi\">4</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">5</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">6</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span><span class=\"mi\">7</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">8</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">9</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Matrix</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℚ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n</div></div>\n<p>Let me walk you through the changes:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>change the type of matrix we're working with: now we're using square matrices of size <code>z</code>. We do this by indexing over the type <code>Fin z</code>, which is constructed as natural numbers less than <code>z</code>, giving it precisely <code>z</code> elements.</li>\n<li>make sure the other parameters fit the previous description</li>\n<li>adapt <code>lessSucc</code>.</li>\n<li>tell lean that this terminates because <code>i</code> keeps getting closer to <code>z</code>, meaning that <code>z - i</code> is decreasing.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>there are some things that might be done in a more consise way:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>there may be a better way to take the successor of <code>i</code> while staying in <code>Fin z</code>, possibly already in mathlib</li>\n<li>in order to prove that these values actually become zero, you will need a stronger assumption on <code>α</code> than just <code>GroupWithZero</code>, <code>Add</code> and <code>Neg</code>; you probably want <code>DivisionRing</code>, if not <code>Field</code>. (if you combine <code>GroupWithZero</code> and <code>AddGroup</code>, lean will be confused about which zero to use.)</li>\n</ul>",
